These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, yellow, turquise
3 different games are played: chess, scrabble, poker
House: wooden, cottage, craftsman
3 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, guinea-pig
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, card-games, puzzles
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, march, september
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bongani, havana
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the craftsman house##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who likes coral is the cottage house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the cain-smoker is the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Color      | coral  | yellow   | turquise      |
| Game          | poker      | chess     | scrabble     |
| House           | cottage | craftsman  | wooden   |
| Pet   | hamster   | guinea-pig     | snake  |
| Hobby   | baking      | card-games      | puzzles      |
| Birthday   | september      | march    | april   |
| Cigar         | cain    | bongani | havana |

