.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, emerald, blood-red
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, gospel, techno
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, march, february
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, mango, lemon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, oliveros, montecristo
3 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, snooker
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes blood-red is the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is the person eating lemon##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
10. the fan of techno is the person eating lettuce##1
11. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Color         | emerald | blood-red  | light-blue     |
| Music-Genre           | soul        | gospel | techno    |
| Flower   | iris  | dahlia    | zinnia    |
| Birthday   | february    | march    | october   |
| Food           | lemon        | mango    | lettuce        |
| Cigar         | oliveros     | bolivar  | montecristo     |
| Game     | snooker         | mah-jongg       | monopoly |

