.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, house
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, november, july
3 different games are played: go, snooker, whist
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, puzzles, drawing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, dahlia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, pall-mall, alhambra
House: wooden, ranch-style, palace
 1. the wooden house is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the fan of house##1
 7. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person playing whist is the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre      | house   | rock         | dubstep |
| Birthday          | july  | november        | march    |
| Game           | go | snooker  | whist  |
| Hobby   | drawing | camping | puzzles         |
| Flower   | azalea | iris       | dahlia        |
| Cigar           | fonseca       | pall-mall        | alhambra       |
| House     | palace       | wooden  | ranch-style       |

