.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, april, october
3 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, chess
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, rose
House: cape-cod, palace, townhouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, airplane, snowmobile
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, turquise, purple
There 3 different types of food: banana, corn, lime
 1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the palace house is the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person eating banana is the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person eating corn is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 8. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
11. the cape-cod house is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
