 8. the futuristic house is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the argentine##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is the colonial house##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the indian##1

