.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, car, van
House: townhouse, wooden, victorian
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, fisherman, doctor
City: hannover, edinburgh, colone
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daffodil, balloon-flower
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, turquise, purple
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, november
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person driving the van is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 4. the wooden house is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 6. the doctor is the person who likes green##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes green##1
 8. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
11. the pilot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
