| Transport      | car       | airplane     | van         |
| House          | wooden      | townhouse  | victorian     |
| Job         | pilot | fisherman     | doctor |
| City   | hannover  | colone | edinburgh     |
| Flower   | lily    | balloon-flower      | daffodil     |
| Color   | turquise  | purple    | green  |
| Birthday           | august   | november      | february      |

 